value.title: InteractAI
value.description:
About Event

​We’re hosting an end-of-year marketers hangout in San Francisco at Standard Deviant Brewing Pier 70, from 4:00 PM to 8:00 PM.

​It’s a relaxed evening to connect with fellow marketers, grab some drinks, and swap real war stories from the year. We’ll talk about what worked, what didn’t, and what’s top of mind as we plan for what’s next.

​Expect thoughtful conversations, an easy going atmosphere, and a chance to meet people building and marketing genuinely great products.
